title: Huskies swept Ferris State after Saretsky scored in double OT - michigantechhuskies.com
content: Huskies swept Ferris State after Saretsky scored in double OT  michigantechhuskies.com
description: Parker Saretsky scored 6:34 into double overtime to send No. 15 Michigan Tech to the CCHA Mason Cup Semifinals
